TripBooks

HTML5 app for calculating shared trip expenses. Simple app (one file), using
local SQL storage.

 * Click the 'Start Trip' button to setup the local SQL database.
 * Enter a transaction
 * TripBooks will keep a tally of total cost / person and how much each
  * person is owed / owes.

Try it out here: http://fattarsi.com/m/html5/tripbooks/
